      "color": "0",
      "text": "# CEX Architecture\n**293 kinds** | **298 builders** | **3,563 ISOs** | **12 pillars** | **8 nuclei** | **135 tools** | **4 runtimes** (Claude / Codex / Gemini / Ollama)"
    },

    {
