      "type": "text",
      "x": 60, "y": -460, "width": 160, "height": 140,
      "color": "0",
      "text": "## N07\n**Orchestrator**\nOrchestrating Sloth\n`Opus 4.6 (1M)`\n*dispatch, never build*"
